beIN SPORTS EN 1.desc_ar: Following their 3-0 win at Anfield in November, Nottingham Forest are looking to complete their first league double over Liverpool since 1962-63. Liverpool have won just one of their last 15 away league games against Nottingham Forest, beating them 1-0 in March 2024 thanks to a late Darwin Núñez strike.

beIN SPORTS EN 1.title_en: Manchester City vs Newcastle United - English Premier League 2025/2026 Week 27 - Mini Match
beIN SPORTS EN 1.title_fr: Manchester City vs Newcastle United - Premier League anglaise 2025/2026 Semaine 27 - Mini Match
beIN SPORTS EN 1.desc_ar: Manchester City are unbeaten in their last 21 Premier League home games against Newcastle, winning each of the last 16. In English top-flight history, only Everton have had a longer winning home run against an opponent. Newcastle are looking to complete their first league double over Manchester City since 1983-84, and first in the top-flight since 1955-56. However, their 20 games at the Etihad Stadium is the most a team has played at a venue without ever winning in Premier League history.
